    "description": "<p>Train Kids Early Intervention and Educare Centre LLP is a specialized educational center that provides early intervention services and student care for children with developmental needs. The center focuses on supporting children in developing essential skills for daily living, academic readiness, and social interaction.<br>\n</p>\n<p>Key Features of Train Kids:<br>\n1.\tEarly Intervention Programs – Designed for young children with developmental delays or special needs, focusing on cognitive, communication, motor, and social-emotional skills.<br>\n2.\tStudent Care Services – A structured after-school program for children aged 7 to 14 years, providing academic support and skill-building activities.<br>\n3.\tStructured Learning Environment – The curriculum incorporates individualized teaching strategies, sensory play, and social skill development.<br>\n</p>",
